</ul>
<h2 id="ưu-điểm" class="toc-header"><a class="toc-anchor" href="#ưu-điểm">¶</a> Ưu điểm</h2>
<ul>
<li>Code đơn giản, dễ hiểu</li>
<li>Không tốn thêm bộ nhớ</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="nhược-điểm" class="toc-header"><a class="toc-anchor" href="#nhược-điểm">¶</a> Nhược điểm</h2>
<ul>
<li>Độ phức tạp <svg style="vertical-align: -0.566ex;" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="6.681ex" height="2.452ex" role="img" focusable="false" viewBox="0 -833.9 2952.8 1083.9" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><defs><path id="MJX-3-TEX-C-4F" d="M308 428Q289 428 289 438Q289 457 318 508T378 593Q417 638 475 671T599 705Q688 705 732 643T777 483Q777 380 733 285T620 123T464 18T293 -22Q188 -22 123 51T58 245Q58 327 87 403T159 533T249 626T333 685T388 705Q404 705 404 693Q404 674 363 649Q333 632 304 606T239 537T181 429T158 290Q158 179 214 114T364 48Q489 48 583 165T677 438Q677 473 670 505T648 568T601 617T528 636Q518 636 513 635Q486 629 460 600T419 544T392 490Q383 470 372 459Q341 430 308 428Z"></path><path id="MJX-3-TEX-N-28" d="M94 250Q94 319 104 381T127 488T164 576T202 643T244 695T277 729T302 750H315H319Q333 750 333 741Q333 738 316 720T275 667T226 581T184 443T167 250T184 58T225 -81T274 -167T316 -220T333 -241Q333 -250 318 -250H315H302L274 -226Q180 -141 137 -14T94 250Z"></path><path id="MJX-3-TEX-I-1D441" d="M234 637Q231 637 226 637Q201 637 196 638T191 649Q191 676 202 682Q204 683 299 683Q376 683 387 683T401 677Q612 181 616 168L670 381Q723 592 723 606Q723 633 659 637Q635 637 635 648Q635 650 637 660Q641 676 643 679T653 683Q656 683 684 682T767 680Q817 680 843 681T873 682Q888 682 888 672Q888 650 880 642Q878 637 858 637Q787 633 769 597L620 7Q618 0 599 0Q585 0 582 2Q579 5 453 305L326 604L261 344Q196 88 196 79Q201 46 268 46H278Q284 41 284 38T282 19Q278 6 272 0H259Q228 2 151 2Q123 2 100 2T63 2T46 1Q31 1 31 10Q31 14 34 26T39 40Q41 46 62 46Q130 49 150 85Q154 91 221 362L289 634Q287 635 234 637Z"></path><path id="MJX-3-TEX-N-32" d="M109 429Q82 429 66 447T50 491Q50 562 103 614T235 666Q326 666 387 610T449 465Q449 422 429 383T381 315T301 241Q265 210 201 149L142 93L218 92Q375 92 385 97Q392 99 409 186V189H449V186Q448 183 436 95T421 3V0H50V19V31Q50 38 56 46T86 81Q115 113 136 137Q145 147 170 174T204 211T233 244T261 278T284 308T305 340T320 369T333 401T340 431T343 464Q343 527 309 573T212 619Q179 619 154 602T119 569T109 550Q109 549 114 549Q132 549 151 535T170 489Q170 464 154 447T109 429Z"></path><path id="MJX-3-TEX-N-29" d="M60 749L64 750Q69 750 74 750H86L114 726Q208 641 251 514T294 250Q294 182 284 119T261 12T224 -76T186 -143T145 -194T113 -227T90 -246Q87 -249 86 -250H74Q66 -250 63 -250T58 -247T55 -238Q56 -237 66 -225Q221 -64 221 250T66 725Q56 737 55 738Q55 746 60 749Z"></path></defs><g stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" transform="scale(1,-1)"><g data-mml-node="math"><g data-mml-node="TeXAtom" data-mjx-texclass="ORD"><g data-mml-node="mi"><use data-c="4F" xlink:href="#MJX-3-TEX-C-4F"></use></g></g><g data-mml-node="mo" transform="translate(796,0)"><use data-c="28" xlink:href="#MJX-3-TEX-N-28"></use></g><g data-mml-node="msup" transform="translate(1185,0)"><g data-mml-node="mi"><use data-c="1D441" xlink:href="#MJX-3-TEX-I-1D441"></use></g><g data-mml-node="mn" transform="translate(975.3,363) scale(0.707)"><use data-c="32" xlink:href="#MJX-3-TEX-N-32"></use></g></g><g data-mml-node="mo" transform="translate(2563.8,0)"><use data-c="29" xlink:href="#MJX-3-TEX-N-29"></use></g></g></g></svg>, không đủ nhanh với dữ liệu lớn.</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="code" class="toc-header"><a class="toc-anchor" href="#code">¶</a> Code</h2>
<pre class="prismjs line-numbers" data-start="1" v-pre="true"><code class="language-cpp">for (int i = 0; i &lt; n; i++)
    for (int j = 0; j &lt; n - 1; j++)
        if (a[j] &gt; a[j+1]) {
            swap(a[j], a[j+1]);
        }
</code></pre>
<h2 id="minh-họa" class="toc-header"><a class="toc-anchor" href="#minh-họa">¶</a> Minh họa</h2>
<p>Bạn có thể vào <a href="http://visualgo.net/sorting" class="is-external-link">VisuAlgo</a>.</p>
<ul>
<li>Chọn <strong>Bubble</strong> ở thanh menu bên trên.</li>
<li>Ấn vào nút <code>Create</code> ở phía dưới trang để tạo một dãy mới</li>
<li>Ấn vào <code>Sort</code>, rồi <code>Go</code> để chạy thuật toán.</li>
</ul>
<h1 id="sắp-xếp-chèn-insertion-sort" class="toc-header"><a class="toc-anchor" href="#sắp-xếp-chèn-insertion-sort">¶</a> Sắp xếp chèn (Insertion Sort)</h1>
<h2 id="ý-tưởng-1" class="toc-header"><a class="toc-anchor" href="#ý-tưởng-1">¶</a> Ý tưởng</h2>
<p>Ý tưởng chính của thuật toán là ta sẽ sắp xếp lần lượt từng đoạn gồm 1 phần tử đầu tiên, 2 phần tử đầu tiên, ..., <svg style="vertical-align: 0;" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="2.009ex" height="1.545ex" role="img" focusable="false" viewBox="0 -683 888 683" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><defs><path id="MJX-4-TEX-I-1D441" d="M234 637Q231 637 226 637Q201 637 196 638T191 649Q191 676 202 682Q204 683 299 683Q376 683 387 683T401 677Q612 181 616 168L670 381Q723 592 723 606Q723 633 659 637Q635 637 635 648Q635 650 637 660Q641 676 643 679T653 683Q656 683 684 682T767 680Q817 680 843 681T873 682Q888 682 888 672Q888 650 880 642Q878 637 858 637Q787 633 769 597L620 7Q618 0 599 0Q585 0 582 2Q579 5 453 305L326 604L261 344Q196 88 196 79Q201 46 268 46H278Q284 41 284 38T282 19Q278 6 272 0H259Q228 2 151 2Q123 2 100 2T63 2T46 1Q31 1 31 10Q31 14 34 26T39 40Q41 46 62 46Q130 49 150 85Q154 91 221 362L289 634Q287 635 234 637Z"></path></defs><g stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" transform="scale(1,-1)"><g data-mml-node="math"><g data-mml-node="mi"><use data-c="1D441" xlink:href="#MJX-4-TEX-I-1D441"></use></g></g></g></svg> phần tử.</p>
<p>Giả sử ta đã sắp xếp xong <svg style="vertical-align: -0.025ex;" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="0.781ex" height="1.52ex" role="img" focusable="false" viewBox="0 -661 345 672" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><defs><path id="MJX-5-TEX-I-1D456" d="M184 600Q184 624 203 642T247 661Q265 661 277 649T290 619Q290 596 270 577T226 557Q211 557 198 567T184 600ZM21 287Q21 295 30 318T54 369T98 420T158 442Q197 442 223 419T250 357Q250 340 236 301T196 196T154 83Q149 61 149 51Q149 26 166 26Q175 26 185 29T208 43T235 78T260 137Q263 149 265 151T282 153Q302 153 302 143Q302 135 293 112T268 61T223 11T161 -11Q129 -11 102 10T74 74Q74 91 79 106T122 220Q160 321 166 341T173 380Q173 404 156 404H154Q124 404 99 371T61 287Q60 286 59 284T58 281T56 279T53 278T49 278T41 278H27Q21 284 21 287Z"></path></defs><g stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" transform="scale(1,-1)"><g data-mml-node="math"><g data-mml-node="mi"><use data-c="1D456" xlink:href="#MJX-5-TEX-I-1D456"></use></g></g></g></svg> phần tử của mảng. Để sắp xếp <svg style="vertical-align: -0.186ex;" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="4.677ex" height="1.692ex" role="img" focusable="false" viewBox="0 -666 2067.4 748" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><defs><path id="MJX-6-TEX-I-1D456" d="M184 600Q184 624 203 642T247 661Q265 661 277 649T290 619Q290 596 270 577T226 557Q211 557 198 567T184 600ZM21 287Q21 295 30 318T54 369T98 420T158 442Q197 442 223 419T250 357Q250 340 236 301T196 196T154 83Q149 61 149 51Q149 26 166 26Q175 26 185 29T208 43T235 78T260 137Q263 149 265 151T282 153Q302 153 302 143Q302 135 293 112T268 61T223 11T161 -11Q129 -11 102 10T74 74Q74 91 79 106T122 220Q160 321 166 341T173 380Q173 404 156 404H154Q124 404 99 371T61 287Q60 286 59 284T58 281T56 279T53 278T49 278T41 278H27Q21 284 21 287Z"></path><path id="MJX-6-TEX-N-2B" d="M56 237T56 250T70 270H369V420L370 570Q380 583 389 583Q402 583 409 568V270H707Q722 262 722 250T707 230H409V-68Q401 -82 391 -82H389H387Q375 -82 369 -68V230H70Q56 237 56 250Z"></path><path id="MJX-6-TEX-N-31" d="M213 578L200 573Q186 568 160 563T102 556H83V602H102Q149 604 189 617T245 641T273 663Q275 666 285 666Q294 666 302 660V361L303 61Q310 54 315 52T339 48T401 46H427V0H416Q395 3 257 3Q121 3 100 0H88V46H114Q136 46 152 46T177 47T193 50T201 52T207 57T213 61V578Z"></path></defs><g stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" transform="scale(1,-1)"><g data-mml-node="math"><g data-mml-node="mi"><use data-c="1D456" xlink:href="#MJX-6-TEX-I-1D456"></use></g><g data-mml-node="mo" transform="translate(567.2,0)"><use data-c="2B" xlink:href="#MJX-6-TEX-N-2B"></use></g><g data-mml-node="mn" transform="translate(1567.4,0)"><use data-c="31" xlink:href="#MJX-6-TEX-N-31"></use></g></g></g></svg> phần tử đầu tiên, ta tìm vị trí phù hợp của phần tử thứ <svg style="vertical-align: -0.186ex;" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="4.677ex" height="1.692ex" role="img" focusable="false" viewBox="0 -666 2067.4 748" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><defs><path id="MJX-7-TEX-I-1D456" d="M184 600Q184 624 203 642T247 661Q265 661 277 649T290 619Q290 596 270 577T226 557Q211 557 198 567T184 600ZM21 287Q21 295 30 318T54 369T98 420T158 442Q197 442 223 419T250 357Q250 340 236 301T196 196T154 83Q149 61 149 51Q149 26 166 26Q175 26 185 29T208 43T235 78T260 137Q263 149 265 151T282 153Q302 153 302 143Q302 135 293 112T268 61T223 11T161 -11Q129 -11 102 10T74 74Q74 91 79 106T122 220Q160 321 166 341T173 380Q173 404 156 404H154Q124 404 99 371T61 287Q60 286 59 284T58 281T56 279T53 278T49 278T41 278H27Q21 284 21 287Z"></path><path id="MJX-7-TEX-N-2B" d="M56 237T56 250T70 270H369V420L370 570Q380 583 389 583Q402 583 409 568V270H707Q722 262 722 250T707 230H409V-68Q401 -82 391 -82H389H387Q375 -82 369 -68V230H70Q56 237 56 250Z"></path><path id="MJX-7-TEX-N-31" d="M213 578L200 573Q186 568 160 563T102 556H83V602H102Q149 604 189 617T245 641T273 663Q275 666 285 666Q294 666 302 660V361L303 61Q310 54 315 52T339 48T401 46H427V0H416Q395 3 257 3Q121 3 100 0H88V46H114Q136 46 152 46T177 47T193 50T201 52T207 57T213 61V578Z"></path></defs><g stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" transform="scale(1,-1)"><g data-mml-node="math"><g data-mml-node="mi"><use data-c="1D456" xlink:href="#MJX-7-TEX-I-1D456"></use></g><g data-mml-node="mo" transform="translate(567.2,0)"><use data-c="2B" xlink:href="#MJX-7-TEX-N-2B"></use></g><g data-mml-node="mn" transform="translate(1567.4,0)"><use data-c="31" xlink:href="#MJX-7-TEX-N-31"></use></g></g></g></svg> và "chèn" nó vào đó.</p>
<h2 id="ưu-điểm-1" class="toc-header"><a class="toc-anchor" href="#ưu-điểm-1">¶</a> Ưu điểm</h2>
<ul>
<li>Nếu danh sách đã gần đúng thứ tự, Insertion Sort sẽ chạy rất nhanh. Ví dụ bạn cần sắp xếp Highscore trong game.</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="nhược-điểm-1" class="toc-header"><a class="toc-anchor" href="#nhược-điểm-1">¶</a> Nhược điểm</h2>
<ul>
<li>Độ phức tạp <svg style="vertical-align: -0.566ex;" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="6.681ex" height="2.452ex" role="img" focusable="false" viewBox="0 -833.9 2952.8 1083.9" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><defs><path id="MJX-8-TEX-C-4F" d="M308 428Q289 428 289 438Q289 457 318 508T378 593Q417 638 475 671T599 705Q688 705 732 643T777 483Q777 380 733 285T620 123T464 18T293 -22Q188 -22 123 51T58 245Q58 327 87 403T159 533T249 626T333 685T388 705Q404 705 404 693Q404 674 363 649Q333 632 304 606T239 537T181 429T158 290Q158 179 214 114T364 48Q489 48 583 165T677 438Q677 473 670 505T648 568T601 617T528 636Q518 636 513 635Q486 629 460 600T419 544T392 490Q383 470 372 459Q341 430 308 428Z"></path><path id="MJX-8-TEX-N-28" d="M94 250Q94 319 104 381T127 488T164 576T202 643T244 695T277 729T302 750H315H319Q333 750 333 741Q333 738 316 720T275 667T226 581T184 443T167 250T184 58T225 -81T274 -167T316 -220T333 -241Q333 -250 318 -250H315H302L274 -226Q180 -141 137 -14T94 250Z"></path><path id="MJX-8-TEX-I-1D441" d="M234 637Q231 637 226 637Q201 637 196 638T191 649Q191 676 202 682Q204 683 299 683Q376 683 387 683T401 677Q612 181 616 168L670 381Q723 592 723 606Q723 633 659 637Q635 637 635 648Q635 650 637 660Q641 676 643 679T653 683Q656 683 684 682T767 680Q817 680 843 681T873 682Q888 682 888 672Q888 650 880 642Q878 637 858 637Q787 633 769 597L620 7Q618 0 599 0Q585 0 582 2Q579 5 453 305L326 604L261 344Q196 88 196 79Q201 46 268 46H278Q284 41 284 38T282 19Q278 6 272 0H259Q228 2 151 2Q123 2 100 2T63 2T46 1Q31 1 31 10Q31 14 34 26T39 40Q41 46 62 46Q130 49 150 85Q154 91 221 362L289 634Q287 635 234 637Z"></path><path id="MJX-8-TEX-N-32" d="M109 429Q82 429 66 447T50 491Q50 562 103 614T235 666Q326 666 387 610T449 465Q449 422 429 383T381 315T301 241Q265 210 201 149L142 93L218 92Q375 92 385 97Q392 99 409 186V189H449V186Q448 183 436 95T421 3V0H50V19V31Q50 38 56 46T86 81Q115 113 136 137Q145 147 170 174T204 211T233 244T261 278T284 308T305 340T320 369T333 401T340 431T343 464Q343 527 309 573T212 619Q179 619 154 602T119 569T109 550Q109 549 114 549Q132 549 151 535T170 489Q170 464 154 447T109 429Z"></path><path id="MJX-8-TEX-N-29" d="M60 749L64 750Q69 750 74 750H86L114 726Q208 641 251 514T294 250Q294 182 284 119T261 12T224 -76T186 -143T145 -194T113 -227T90 -246Q87 -249 86 -250H74Q66 -250 63 -250T58 -247T55 -238Q56 -237 66 -225Q221 -64 221 250T66 725Q56 737 55 738Q55 746 60 749Z"></path></defs><g stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" transform="scale(1,-1)"><g data-mml-node="math"><g data-mml-node="TeXAtom" data-mjx-texclass="ORD"><g data-mml-node="mi"><use data-c="4F" xlink:href="#MJX-8-TEX-C-4F"></use></g></g><g data-mml-node="mo" transform="translate(796,0)"><use data-c="28" xlink:href="#MJX-8-TEX-N-28"></use></g><g data-mml-node="msup" transform="translate(1185,0)"><g data-mml-node="mi"><use data-c="1D441" xlink:href="#MJX-8-TEX-I-1D441"></use></g><g data-mml-node="mn" transform="translate(975.3,363) scale(0.707)"><use data-c="32" xlink:href="#MJX-8-TEX-N-32"></use></g></g><g data-mml-node="mo" transform="translate(2563.8,0)"><use data-c="29" xlink:href="#MJX-8-TEX-N-29"></use></g></g></g></svg>, không đủ nhanh với dữ liệu lớn.</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="code-1" class="toc-header"><a class="toc-anchor" href="#code-1">¶</a> Code</h2>
<pre class="prismjs line-numbers" data-start="1" v-pre="true"><code class="language-cpp">for (int i = 1; i &lt; n; i++) {
    // Tìm vị trí phù hợp cho i
    int j = i;
    while (j &gt; 0 &amp;&amp; data[i] &lt; data[j-1]) --j;

    // Đưa i về đúng vị trí
    int tmp = data[i];
    for (int k = i; k &gt; j; k--)
        data[k] = data[k-1];
    data[j] = tmp;
}
</code></pre>
<h2 id="minh-họa-1" class="toc-header"><a class="toc-anchor" href="#minh-họa-1">¶</a> Minh họa</h2>
<p>Bạn có thể vào <a href="http://visualgo.net/sorting" class="is-external-link">VisuAlgo</a>.</p>
<ul>
<li>Chọn <strong>Insert</strong> ở thanh menu bên trên.</li>
<li>Ấn vào nút <code>Create</code> ở phía dưới trang để tạo một dãy mới</li>
<li>Ấn vào <code>Sort</code>, rồi <code>Go</code> để chạy thuật toán.</li>
</ul>
<h1 id="sắp-xếp-trộn-merge-sort" class="toc-header"><a class="toc-anchor" href="#sắp-xếp-trộn-merge-sort">¶</a> Sắp xếp trộn (Merge sort)</h1>
<h2 id="ý-tưởng-2" class="toc-header"><a class="toc-anchor" href="#ý-tưởng-2">¶</a> Ý tưởng</h2>
<p>Sắp xếp trộn hoạt động kiểu đệ quy:</p>
<ul>
<li>Đầu tiên chia dữ liệu thành 2 phần, và sắp xếp từng phần.</li>
<li>Sau đó gộp 2 phần lại với nhau. Để gộp 2 phần, ta làm như sau:
<ul>
<li>Tạo một dãy <svg style="vertical-align: 0;" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1.697ex" height="1.62ex" role="img" focusable="false" viewBox="0 -716 750 716" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><defs><path id="MJX-9-TEX-I-1D434" d="M208 74Q208 50 254 46Q272 46 272 35Q272 34 270 22Q267 8 264 4T251 0Q249 0 239 0T205 1T141 2Q70 2 50 0H42Q35 7 35 11Q37 38 48 46H62Q132 49 164 96Q170 102 345 401T523 704Q530 716 547 716H555H572Q578 707 578 706L606 383Q634 60 636 57Q641 46 701 46Q726 46 726 36Q726 34 723 22Q720 7 718 4T704 0Q701 0 690 0T651 1T578 2Q484 2 455 0H443Q437 6 437 9T439 27Q443 40 445 43L449 46H469Q523 49 533 63L521 213H283L249 155Q208 86 208 74ZM516 260Q516 271 504 416T490 562L463 519Q447 492 400 412L310 260L413 259Q516 259 516 260Z"></path></defs><g stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" transform="scale(1,-1)"><g data-mml-node="math"><g data-mml-node="mi"><use data-c="1D434" xlink:href="#MJX-9-TEX-I-1D434"></use></g></g></g></svg> mới để chứa các phần tử đã sắp xếp.</li>
<li>So sánh 2 phần tử đầu tiên của 2 phần. Phần tử nhỏ hơn ta cho vào <svg style="vertical-align: 0;" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1.697ex" height="1.62ex" role="img" focusable="false" viewBox="0 -716 750 716" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><defs><path id="MJX-10-TEX-I-1D434" d="M208 74Q208 50 254 46Q272 46 272 35Q272 34 270 22Q267 8 264 4T251 0Q249 0 239 0T205 1T141 2Q70 2 50 0H42Q35 7 35 11Q37 38 48 46H62Q132 49 164 96Q170 102 345 401T523 704Q530 716 547 716H555H572Q578 707 578 706L606 383Q634 60 636 57Q641 46 701 46Q726 46 726 36Q726 34 723 22Q720 7 718 4T704 0Q701 0 690 0T651 1T578 2Q484 2 455 0H443Q437 6 437 9T439 27Q443 40 445 43L449 46H469Q523 49 533 63L521 213H283L249 155Q208 86 208 74ZM516 260Q516 271 504 416T490 562L463 519Q447 492 400 412L310 260L413 259Q516 259 516 260Z"></path></defs><g stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" transform="scale(1,-1)"><g data-mml-node="math"><g data-mml-node="mi"><use data-c="1D434" xlink:href="#MJX-10-TEX-I-1D434"></use></g></g></g></svg> và xóa khỏi phần tương ứng.</li>
<li>Tiếp tục như vậy đến khi ta cho hết các phần tử vào dãy <svg style="vertical-align: 0;" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1.697ex" height="1.62ex" role="img" focusable="false" viewBox="0 -716 750 716" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><defs><path id="MJX-11-TEX-I-1D434" d="M208 74Q208 50 254 46Q272 46 272 35Q272 34 270 22Q267 8 264 4T251 0Q249 0 239 0T205 1T141 2Q70 2 50 0H42Q35 7 35 11Q37 38 48 46H62Q132 49 164 96Q170 102 345 401T523 704Q530 716 547 716H555H572Q578 707 578 706L606 383Q634 60 636 57Q641 46 701 46Q726 46 726 36Q726 34 723 22Q720 7 718 4T704 0Q701 0 690 0T651 1T578 2Q484 2 455 0H443Q437 6 437 9T439 27Q443 40 445 43L449 46H469Q523 49 533 63L521 213H283L249 155Q208 86 208 74ZM516 260Q516 271 504 416T490 562L463 519Q447 492 400 412L310 260L413 259Q516 259 516 260Z"></path></defs><g stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" transform="scale(1,-1)"><g data-mml-node="math"><g data-mml-node="mi"><use data-c="1D434" xlink:href="#MJX-11-TEX-I-1D434"></use></g></g></g></svg>.</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="ưu-điểm-2" class="toc-header"><a class="toc-anchor" href="#ưu-điểm-2">¶</a> Ưu điểm</h2>
<ul>
<li>Chạy nhanh, độ phức tạp <svg style="vertical-align: -0.566ex;" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="12.567ex" height="2.262ex" role="img" focusable="false" viewBox="0 -750 5554.4 1000" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><defs><path id="MJX-12-TEX-C-4F" d="M308 428Q289 428 289 438Q289 457 318 508T378 593Q417 638 475 671T599 705Q688 705 732 643T777 483Q777 380 733 285T620 123T464 18T293 -22Q188 -22 123 51T58 245Q58 327 87 403T159 533T249 626T333 685T388 705Q404 705 404 693Q404 674 363 649Q333 632 304 606T239 537T181 429T158 290Q158 179 214 114T364 48Q489 48 583 165T677 438Q677 473 670 505T648 568T601 617T528 636Q518 636 513 635Q486 629 460 600T419 544T392 490Q383 470 372 459Q341 430 308 428Z"></path><path id="MJX-12-TEX-N-28" d="M94 250Q94 319 104 381T127 488T164 576T202 643T244 695T277 729T302 750H315H319Q333 750 333 741Q333 738 316 720T275 667T226 581T184 443T167 250T184 58T225 -81T274 -167T316 -220T333 -241Q333 -250 318 -250H315H302L274 -226Q180 -141 137 -14T94 250Z"></path><path id="MJX-12-TEX-I-1D441" d="M234 637Q231 637 226 637Q201 637 196 638T191 649Q191 676 202 682Q204 683 299 683Q376 683 387 683T401 677Q612 181 616 168L670 381Q723 592 723 606Q723 633 659 637Q635 637 635 648Q635 650 637 660Q641 676 643 679T653 683Q656 683 684 682T767 680Q817 680 843 681T873 682Q888 682 888 672Q888 650 880 642Q878 637 858 637Q787 633 769 597L620 7Q618 0 599 0Q585 0 582 2Q579 5 453 305L326 604L261 344Q196 88 196 79Q201 46 268 46H278Q284 41 284 38T282 19Q278 6 272 0H259Q228 2 151 2Q123 2 100 2T63 2T46 1Q31 1 31 10Q31 14 34 26T39 40Q41 46 62 46Q130 49 150 85Q154 91 221 362L289 634Q287 635 234 637Z"></path><path id="MJX-12-TEX-N-2217" d="M229 286Q216 420 216 436Q216 454 240 464Q241 464 245 464T251 465Q263 464 273 456T283 436Q283 419 277 356T270 286L328 328Q384 369 389 372T399 375Q412 375 423 365T435 338Q435 325 425 315Q420 312 357 282T289 250L355 219L425 184Q434 175 434 161Q434 146 425 136T401 125Q393 125 383 131T328 171L270 213Q283 79 283 63Q283 53 276 44T250 35Q2